    "comment": "Rationale: Figure S2B: Lnx1 was detected in PSD biochemical fractions from mouse hippocampi. The antibody shows an unspecific band, the other band (presumably Lnx1) is abolished in controls using Lnx1 -/- mice.\n\nFigure S2C: confocal imaging of Thy1-GFP-M, synapsin1 and overexpressed Flag-Lnx1 in cultured hippocampal neurons showed localization to dendritic spines.. Experimental description: Supplementary Figure S2 legend: \"(A) Specific postnatal expression of Lnx1 in hippocampus was identified with quantitatively immunoprecipitated (IP) β-gal protein in hippocampal lysates from Lnx1 +/+ or Lnx1 -/- mice during development.\"",
